    <p>Click the <strong>Add Conference</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="enable_recording" data-step-uuid="56723CAE-B4AF-4AF9-A6D5-5DCB488CDAC7">
    <h2 id="enable_recording" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Enable Recording</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/698/999/original/9cf239db-ccc2-4de7-9195-29e158da130d.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/698/999/medium/9cf239db-ccc2-4de7-9195-29e158da130d.png" srcset="" alt="Enable Recording" height="472" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E4B9E810-1EE7-0135-8DCF-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p> To turn on the options for recording within the conference, click the <strong>Enable recording for this conference </strong>checkbox.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="update_conference" data-step-uuid="A1F2A4A6-6142-4514-A17C-29B06808E5F2">
    <h2 id="update_conference" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Save Conference</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/005/699/001/original/21aaa755-87fb-4057-9e53-1666face8938.png" srcset="" alt="Save Conference" height="77" width="194">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_E4BA1DC0-1EE7-0135-8DD1-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the<strong> Save</strong> button.</p>
<p>Once you <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-start-a-conference/ta-p/1074" target="_blank">start your conference</a>, you can start and stop the recording as necessary in the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Conferences-interface-as-a-moderator-or/ta-p/1072" target="_blank">Conferences interface</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>Completed recordings may take some time to render.</p>
  </div>
